Yes, yes.

04:00:13.968 --> 04:00:15.303
One, two.

04:00:15.386 --> 04:00:16.763
Be careful, be careful.

04:00:16.846 --> 04:00:18.097
Ugh, damn it.

04:00:19.474 --> 04:00:20.600
Where's the salt?

04:00:20.683 --> 04:00:21.517
Salt?

04:00:23.186 --> 04:00:24.062
It's in the office.

04:00:25.229 --> 04:00:26.397
You two, go mix some salt water.

04:00:28.232 --> 04:00:29.567
Find a bucket and put all the salt in.

04:00:29.650 --> 04:00:30.777
Yes.

04:00:30.860 --> 04:00:31.694
Let's go.
Oh.

04:00:31.778 --> 04:00:32.987
Uh, it's in the corner.

04:00:33.071 --> 04:00:33.988
Yes.
Yes.

04:00:35.490 --> 04:00:36.532
Ugh, damn it.

04:00:43.581 --> 04:00:44.582
Hyun-ju, are you okay?

04:00:45.249 --> 04:00:46.918
Uh, are you okay, oppa?

04:00:47.001 --> 04:00:47.835
Uh.

04:00:49.670 --> 04:00:51.506
We caught Im Jang-do.

04:00:51.589 --> 04:00:53.466
Yeah.
What about Kim Jun-min?

04:00:53.549 --> 04:00:56.344
Uh, I was outside so I didn't see him, but they caught him.

04:00:56.427 --> 04:00:57.512
Uh.

04:00:57.595 --> 04:00:59.305
Did they kill him, by any chance?

04:01:05.770 --> 04:01:07.230
Hey, let's just make the salt water quickly.

04:01:07.313 --> 04:01:08.731
Find it.
Yeah.

04:01:12.735 --> 04:01:14.445
This should work.

04:01:14.529 --> 04:01:16.030
Water?
I saw it downstairs.

04:01:16.114 --> 04:01:16.948
Let's go down.

04:01:17.031 --> 04:01:17.865
Hyun-ju, let's go.

04:01:32.797 --> 04:01:33.756
Yes.

04:01:33.840 --> 04:01:36.676
Uh, I'll arrive in 5 minutes, so shake him up a bit.

04:01:36.759 --> 04:01:37.927
Ah, and,

04:01:39.095 --> 04:01:41.097
