04:02:03.536 --> 04:02:05.121
Will Hyun-ju be okay?

04:02:07.415 --> 04:02:08.958
Welcome.
This way.

04:02:23.681 --> 04:02:24.515
Stop.

04:02:25.099 --> 04:02:26.184
Let's look at the stairs too.

04:02:26.267 --> 04:02:27.894
Ah, there are no cameras
in that area.

04:02:28.519 --> 04:02:29.353
