04:02:33.274 --> 04:02:34.692
What do you mean by that? Damn it!

04:02:35.776 --> 04:02:37.570
Uh, from outside,

04:02:38.446 --> 04:02:40.156
aren't there cameras that
view the hospital building?

04:02:40.865 --> 04:02:42.450
For that,
you have to go to the police station.

04:02:50.625 --> 04:02:52.376
What about Jun-min?

04:02:54.378 --> 04:02:55.588
He's still unconscious.

04:02:56.797 --> 04:02:58.299
Go to the apartment management office

04:02:58.382 --> 04:03:01.385
