Yes.

04:03:03.137 --> 04:03:04.222
Should I put it here?

04:03:04.305 --> 04:03:06.307
Hey, grab it.
How much should I put in?

04:03:06.849 --> 04:03:08.434
Ah, didn't you
say to put it all in earlier?

04:03:09.143 --> 04:03:10.228
This is too much.

04:03:11.520 --> 04:03:13.481
Let's just put it all in, bro.
You answered earlier.

04:03:14.398 --> 04:03:15.441
Alright.

04:03:18.653 --> 04:03:19.612
What are you doing?

04:03:19.695 --> 04:03:21.155
Making salt water.

04:03:26.911 --> 04:03:27.870
Uh, salt water.

04:03:27.954 --> 04:03:29.080
Oh, yes.

04:03:33.209 --> 04:03:34.377
Come here and look at this.

04:03:36.170 --> 04:03:37.004
Why?

04:03:37.088 --> 04:03:38.673
The boss told us to look.

04:37:46.472 --> 04:37:50.059
I hate people who open their mouth and then close it again the most.

04:37:51.310 --> 04:37:52.144
So,

04:37:52.228 --> 04:37:54.814
if you're determined to tell me everything,

04:37:54.897 --> 04:37:56.649
nod your head.

04:37:57.275 --> 04:37:59.402
If you say you'll talk and then clam up,

04:37:59.485 --> 04:38:01.028
I'll cut off your lips with a knife.

04:38:01.112 --> 04:38:02.029
Understood?

04:38:40.651 --> 04:38:41.986
You're not going to talk, are you?

04:39:29.325 --> 04:39:30.159
Hey.

04:39:30.659 --> 04:39:31.660
Yeah.

04:39:48.052 --> 04:39:49.136
Uh...

04:39:49.720 --> 04:39:50.721
H-Hyun-ju, that...

04:40:05.194 --> 04:40:06.695
Why did he tell us to watch that?

04:40:07.530 --> 04:40:10.616
By now, Myeong-gil must have started looking for Im Jang-do.

04:40:10.699 --> 04:40:13.411
There isn't much time.

04:40:13.494 --> 04:40:16.288
I want to teach you guys something.

04:40:16.372 --> 04:40:18.499
What do you mean?

04:40:18.582 --> 04:40:21.252
This will only end when someone dies.

04:40:21.335 --> 04:40:23.754
I can't guarantee that I'll be alive.

04:40:23.838 --> 04:40:25.631
Ah, we'll win.

04:40:25.714 --> 04:40:27.174
Why are you only thinking negatively?

04:40:27.258 --> 04:40:28.217
Hyun-ju.

04:40:28.300 --> 04:40:29.343
Ah, that's enough.

04:40:35.141 --> 04:40:36.058
Hyun-ju!

04:40:39.437 --> 04:40:41.105
Driver Oh, please take care of Hyun-ju.

04:40:41.188 --> 04:40:42.064
Yes, boss.

04:40:43.399 --> 04:40:45.067
Ah, that kid, really.

04:40:48.863 --> 04:40:49.697
Uh, Geon-woo.

04:40:49.780 --> 04:40:50.781
Oh, yes.

04:40:52.783 --> 04:40:53.659
Uh, if,

04:40:55.744 --> 04:40:57.079
Myeong-gil and you guys

04:40:58.164 --> 04:40:59.999
end up fighting, you,

04:41:01.292 --> 04:41:02.668
you can protect the kids, right?

04:41:04.962 --> 04:41:06.338
I will protect them until the end.

04:41:07.882 --> 04:41:08.966
Alright, thank you.

04:41:10.593 --> 04:41:12.178
Uh, we don't have much time,

04:41:12.803 --> 04:41:14.638
so I'll just teach you one thing.

04:41:18.225 --> 04:41:20.519
To defeat a tightly-knit organization,

04:41:21.270 --> 04:41:22.396
two things are needed.

04:41:24.273 --> 04:41:25.149
Dispersion,

04:41:25.691 --> 04:41:26.692
and division.

04:41:28.360 --> 04:41:31.030
People trust those who know them well
and empathize with them.

04:41:31.113 --> 04:41:32.448
That's how it is.

04:41:34.575 --> 04:41:36.619
If you can't gain individual trust,

04:41:38.287 --> 04:41:40.331
you can't divide the organization.

04:41:55.387 --> 04:41:56.305
Take this off.

04:42:12.404 --> 04:42:14.073
Im Jang-do?

04:42:15.115 --> 04:42:16.867
Among Myeong-gil's subordinates,

04:42:16.951 --> 04:42:20.788
I think you understand Myeong-gil
most accurately.

04:42:21.997 --> 04:42:24.917
Myeong-gil is a very violent
and cruel person.

04:42:25.000 --> 04:42:27.503
But he reads people's minds
like a ghost.

04:42:28.671 --> 04:42:30.256
He knows how to gain.

04:42:31.257 --> 04:42:32.883
That's why
Kim Jun-min and Kang In-beom

04:42:33.384 --> 04:42:35.219
probably truly believe him.

04:42:35.928 --> 04:42:37.221
But you're smart.

04:42:37.805 --> 04:42:39.682
You know Myeong-gil better than them.

04:42:40.599 --> 04:42:41.725
Uh, Myeong-gil

04:42:41.809 --> 04:42:44.562
never empathizes passionately
from the heart.

04:42:45.312 --> 04:42:47.106
He only empathizes coldly with his mind.

04:42:47.189 --> 04:42:48.816
Even normally, he's always

04:42:49.441 --> 04:42:52.236
calculating how to use people.

04:42:52.319 --> 04:42:55.656
You knew that, but you still
went under Myeong-gil.

04:42:56.448 --> 04:42:57.283
Why?

04:42:58.576 --> 04:43:00.452
The first reason is money.

04:43:02.079 --> 04:43:04.415
Myeong-gil gave you a salary
that you would earn in 5 years

04:43:04.498 --> 04:43:06.166
working at a large corporation, didn't he?

04:43:06.709 --> 04:43:10.129
You wanted power after graduating from police academy,
but you were demoted,

04:43:10.212 --> 04:43:12.673
so you had to earn money.

04:43:12.756 --> 04:43:15.009
That way, you wouldn't lose face.

04:43:17.344 --> 04:43:18.178
However,

04:43:18.262 --> 04:43:21.390
the real reason you went under Myeong-gil
is the second one.

04:43:21.974 --> 04:43:25.185
You were confident that you wouldn't be used by Myeong-gil.

04:43:25.769 --> 04:43:27.146
You were certain you wouldn't lose to

04:43:28.230 --> 04:43:29.773
a criminal bastard like him.

04:43:30.816 --> 04:43:33.652
If, by any chance, Myeong-gil has a motive to kill you,

04:43:33.736 --> 04:43:34.987
then at that moment,

04:43:35.070 --> 04:43:37.114
you'd take the money you've earned from Myeong-gil

04:43:38.157 --> 04:43:39.908
and flee to Southeast Asia.

04:43:43.495 --> 04:43:45.164
Yes, your plan is very good.

04:43:46.457 --> 04:43:47.708
But right now, if I

04:43:48.334 --> 04:43:50.586
take a picture of you
and send it to Myeong-gil,

04:43:52.046 --> 04:43:54.381
and say you told me the names of the people
Myeong-gil ordered to be killed,

04:43:54.465 --> 04:43:57.259
Myeong-gil will definitely believe me.

04:43:57.343 --> 04:43:59.345
Because looking at your current state,

04:43:59.428 --> 04:44:01.597
your motive to talk is perfect.

04:44:04.183 --> 04:44:05.017
Then Myeong-gil will

04:44:05.100 --> 04:44:07.811
send back the men he sent to find you,

04:44:07.895 --> 04:44:10.689
and send his hunting dogs
to kill you and bury you secretly.

04:44:10.773 --> 04:44:12.441
They won't give you time to explain to Myeong-gil.

04:44:13.734 --> 04:44:16.945
Myeong-gil told them not to.
Myeong-gil doesn't care about the truth.

04:44:17.029 --> 04:44:18.989
It's just safest to bury you.

04:44:19.073 --> 04:44:21.367
Well, anyway,

04:44:21.992 --> 04:44:24.536
the one who knows most about the crimes
Myeong-gil has committed so far

04:44:24.620 --> 04:44:25.746
isn't Kim Jun-min or Kang In-beom.

04:44:25.829 --> 04:44:29.291
It's you.

04:42:5.897 --> 04:42:32.211
You know Myeong-gil as well as I do.

04:42:36.757 --> 04:42:38.967
If I were to just taint you

04:42:40.511 --> 04:42:41.512
with a very, very small amount of suspicion...

04:42:42.096 --> 04:42:45.057
Myeong-gil will kill you.

04:42:47.768 --> 04:42:49.353
Damn it.

04:42:49.436 --> 04:42:51.105
Wait, damn it.

04:42:53.065 --> 04:42:55.067
Why would I die?!

04:42:55.150 --> 04:42:56.527
You bastard!

04:42:57.403 --> 04:42:59.446
Damn it!

04:42:59.530 --> 04:43:0.406
Im Jang-do!

04:43:02.032 --> 04:43:03.826
Listen to me carefully!

04:43:03.909 --> 04:43:06.537
If you don't get a grip right now,
you'll really die!

04:43:11.417 --> 04:43:12.960
Tell me everything you know.

04:43:14.586 --> 04:43:17.047
Then I'll get you enough money
to live on for the rest of your life

04:43:17.548 --> 04:43:19.133
and send you to a safe country.

04:43:20.551 --> 04:43:22.845
Myeong-gil learned everything from me.

04:43:23.804 --> 04:43:26.348
I know all the places Myeong-gil doesn't know about.

04:43:27.057 --> 04:43:28.142
I promise you.

04:43:32.020 --> 04:43:35.065
You were going to exit anyway.

04:43:36.483 --> 04:43:38.068
Think of this as your chance.

04:43:43.824 --> 04:43:44.783
If I confess,

04:43:46.535 --> 04:43:47.828
how much will you give me?

04:43:50.998 --> 04:43:52.750
Answer quickly and honestly.

04:43:59.965 --> 04:44:03.135
I'm going to finish Myeong-gil
and Smile Capital completely.

04:44:04.178 --> 04:44:05.721
When the job is done, I'll send you to Guam.

04:44:05.804 --> 04:44:07.389
I know some people there.

04:44:08.182 --> 04:44:10.184
I'll support you with everything I have

04:44:10.267 --> 04:44:11.810
so you can start a new life there.

04:46:20.402 --> 04:46:21.528
Uh, get some clothes.

04:46:36.668 --> 04:46:38.378
How long have you been working for Myeong-gil?

04:46:39.463 --> 04:46:40.506
5 years.

04:46:40.589 --> 04:46:42.341
What exactly do you do?

04:46:42.925 --> 04:46:44.718
I prevent Manager Kim's illegal activities

04:46:44.802 --> 04:46:46.595
from reaching the police investigation,

04:46:46.678 --> 04:46:48.055
and if they do,

04:46:48.722 --> 04:46:50.182
I stop them from breaking out.

04:46:50.265 --> 04:46:51.809
Have you ever directly participated?

04:46:51.892 --> 04:46:54.186
For minor cases, In-beom and I sometimes go,

04:46:54.853 --> 04:46:57.523
but mostly it's handled by the subcontracting company
that Manager Kim operates.

04:46:58.148 --> 04:46:59.399
Minor cases?

04:46:59.483 --> 04:47:00.317
Well...

04:47:01.944 --> 04:47:03.987
We sometimes film
evidence videos and things like that.

04:47:04.071 --> 04:47:06.406
You blackmailed Ail Group, didn't you?

04:47:09.243 --> 04:47:10.244
What did you do?

04:47:11.328 --> 04:47:12.913
Manager Kim ordered me to do it.

04:47:12.996 --> 04:47:15.707
I didn't ask who ordered you, I asked what you did.

04:47:17.709 --> 04:47:19.711
I caught Ail Group's eldest son and filmed something.

04:47:19.795 --> 04:47:20.921
What?

04:47:21.713 --> 04:47:23.966
I just stripped him

04:47:24.049 --> 04:47:25.342
and filmed a video.

04:47:25.425 --> 04:47:26.260
Why?

04:47:28.971 --> 04:47:31.056
Tell me about this from the beginning.

04:47:32.724 --> 04:47:35.686
There's a 40-story boutique hotel being built in Gangnam,

04:47:35.769 --> 04:47:38.564
but construction was halted when the company went bankrupt due to COVID-19.

04:47:39.731 --> 04:47:41.567
Manager Kim heard that Ail Group's eldest son
was trying to acquire it,

04:47:41.650 --> 04:47:43.944
but he was 100 billion won short.

04:47:44.027 --> 04:47:45.279
From whom?

04:47:45.946 --> 04:47:47.906
Since the building had been abandoned for so long and become an eyesore,

04:47:47.990 --> 04:47:49.491
the Seoul City government got involved,

04:47:49.575 --> 04:47:51.535
and while looking for someone with cash,

04:47:51.618 --> 04:47:53.871
a National Assembly member who plays golf with Manager Kim every week

04:47:53.954 --> 04:47:56.456
recommended Manager Kim to the mayor.

04:47:57.124 --> 04:47:57.958
Manager Kim's

04:47:58.834 --> 04:48:01.169
dream is to build a casino in the hotel.

04:48:03.213 --> 04:48:06.216
The Seoul City government also promised to
immediately issue a casino license for foreigners,

04:48:06.300 --> 04:48:08.343
so Manager Kim
was excited,

04:48:08.427 --> 04:48:10.554
but then Ail Group's eldest son
suddenly tried to back out,

04:48:10.637 --> 04:48:13.056
so he had me
force him to stay.

04:48:13.932 --> 04:48:16.184
How many people did you film?

04:48:16.935 --> 04:48:17.769
50 people.

04:48:19.187 --> 04:48:21.481
And Myeong-gil is keeping those videos?

04:48:21.565 --> 04:48:22.399
Yes.

04:48:23.358 --> 04:48:25.819
He believes everyone's weakness is money.

04:48:26.695 --> 04:48:27.779
And,

04:48:28.363 --> 04:48:30.908
he never shares anything that can make money.

04:48:31.533 --> 04:48:33.368
Uh, where are those files?

04:48:35.287 --> 04:48:38.373
He keeps the hard drive in a small safe
inside Manager Kim's bedroom.

04:48:38.457 --> 04:48:41.001
But that safe is a German smart safe.

04:48:41.501 --> 04:48:43.462
It only opens with Manager Kim's
right palm vein,

04:48:44.254 --> 04:48:46.548
and if something happens,
he can remotely control it with his phone

04:48:47.174 --> 04:48:49.343
and burn whatever is stored inside the safe.

04:48:49.426 --> 04:48:51.845
There's liquid fuel in the safe ceiling,

04:48:51.929 --> 04:48:54.723
and when you press a button, it drops and catches fire.

04:48:54.806 --> 04:48:57.309
He knows that hard drive is a double-edged sword.

04:48:57.392 --> 04:48:59.144
It's a weapon if you have it, but

04:48:59.227 --> 04:49:01.229
it's evidence if the police seize it.

04:49:02.856 --> 04:49:03.857
That subcontracting company,

04:49:04.608 --> 04:49:05.442
are they thugs?

04:49:05.984 --> 04:49:06.818
Yes.

04:49:07.361 --> 04:49:08.195
How many people?

04:49:08.779 --> 04:49:10.656
I think there are about 30 people.

04:49:10.739 --> 04:49:12.157
Well, they call for more when needed.

04:49:12.240 --> 04:49:13.325
Who's the leader?

04:49:13.909 --> 04:49:14.952
Team Leader Jeong, they call him.

04:49:15.452 --> 04:49:17.579
He's the head of that company,
and he's Manager Kim's butcher.

04:49:17.663 --> 04:49:19.539
He was a mixed martial arts fighter,

04:49:19.623 --> 04:49:22.709
but he killed someone during a match
and had his fighter's license revoked.

04:49:22.793 --> 04:49:24.670
I heard Manager Kim scouted him.

04:49:24.753 --> 04:49:26.380
How does he dispose of bodies?

04:49:27.047 --> 04:49:28.840
Team Leader Jeong handles that side of things.

04:49:29.466 --> 04:49:31.134
Alright, tell me what you know.

04:49:32.594 --> 04:49:33.595
About 3 years ago,

04:49:34.429 --> 04:49:36.306
Manager Kim got angry while drinking once

04:49:36.807 --> 04:49:38.183
and beat someone to death.

04:49:38.767 --> 04:49:40.894
I happened to be nearby,

04:49:40.978 --> 04:49:43.730
so I was managing the situation
until Team Leader Jeong arrived.

04:49:43.814 --> 04:49:47.067
Team Leader Jeong called a fish truck
with a 3-ton tank,

04:49:47.150 --> 04:49:47.985
and took the body away.

04:49:48.527 --> 04:49:50.445
From what I saw of Team Leader Jeong and the driver talking,

04:49:50.529 --> 04:49:52.155
it seemed like they were a regular company they used.

04:49:52.239 --> 04:49:53.907
Their name?

04:49:55.617 --> 04:49:57.160
It's been so long, I don't remember.

0449:58.996 --> 04:50:59.955
Alright.

0450:0.747 --> 04:50:2.374
I know a hospital in Incheon.

0450:2.916 --> 04:50:5.252
I'll call an ambulance for you there, so go and rest.

0450:5.335 --> 04:50:6.545
When the job is done

0450:7.421 --> 04:50:8.422
and things are settled,

0450:9.047 --> 04:50:10.799
I'll send your passport and flight tickets.

0450:15.137 --> 04:50:16.888
Don't contact anyone.

0450:18.140 --> 04:50:19.391
Kim Myeong-gil will find you.

0450:24.771 --> 04:50:26.690
I'm taking your phone.

0450:34.031 --> 04:50:35.782
Let me ask one more thing.

0450:37.701 --> 04:50:39.870
Where are the gold bars Myeong-gil collected?

0450:41.663 --> 04:50:43.248
Only In-beom knows that.

0450:44.541 --> 04:50:45.834
What's their relationship?

0450:45.917 --> 04:50:48.920
In-beom is the only person Manager Kim truly trusts.

0450:49.004 --> 04:51:1.089
I heard they met in prison
and saved each other's lives multiple times.

0451:1.173 --> 04:51:3.425
In-beom will even sacrifice his life.

0451:3.508 --> 04:51:5.802
I can't know all of Manager Kim's true feelings, but

0451:6.928 --> 04:51:8.638
he definitely cherishes In-beom like a brother.
